   <title><![CDATA[Law and Cosmology [God, Law, and Liberty]]]></title>
   <link>https://app.dropwave.io/episode/09a2f5f1-3cf1-4962-a1f8-bae457973487/law-and-cosmology.mp3</link>
   <description><![CDATA[<p>We think we know what law is, but perhaps not. Law has always been rooted in an understanding of the nature of the cosmos, what it is for, and how it works, i.e., cosmology. &nbsp;Two cosmologies are and always have been at war with one another, and, in today&rsquo;s podcast, David will use the preface to Berman&rsquo;s Law and Revolution to explain the challenge we have in thinking of law cosmologically.</p>]]></description>
